  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p585889/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img height=\"509\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201403/004f440aa92344ff864077f2a304e94d.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tKaley Cuoco is glowing pink while holding hands with her handsome husband Ryan Sweeting on Tuesday in New York City.周二，Kaley Cuoco身着粉色裙装和丈夫Ryan Sweeting携手出现在纽约。</p>\n<p>\n\tLater in the day, the 28-year-old actress and the 26-year-old tennis player were spotted checking out of the London Hotel in the Big Apple.当天晚些时候，这位28岁女演员和26岁网球男选手一起在纽约的伦敦酒店办理入住手续。</p>\n<p>\n\tOn the same day, Kaley rocks some navy blue while exiting the CBS This Morning to chatting about the new season of her hit show Big Bang Theory and her marriage to Ryan.同一天，Kaley身穿一身海军蓝的衣服出现在CBS早间谈话节目，宣传《生活大爆炸》的最新季和分享她和Ryan的新婚生活。</p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Ryan and I met and it was completely hearts in our eyes and I get emotional talking about it because he&rsquo;s the most wonderful person in the world. We couldn&rsquo;t be happier,&rdquo; Kaley shared on the show.&ldquo;Ryan和我完全是一见钟情，对我来说，他就是全世界最完美的男人。我们在一起的日子是我最幸福的日子。&rdquo;Kaley在当天的访谈节目中说。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p585889/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p585889\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p586181/\">奥斯卡瞬间：心酸的莱昂纳多 疯狂的自拍</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p586205/\">精彩短片：5分钟浓缩恋爱全过程（视频）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p586104/\">第86届奥斯卡获奖名单:《地心引力》横扫7奖</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en